      "review_text": "Inside pulls you in with its dark, unique vibe and keeps you hooked with constant tension. The strange world raises questions at every step, but in the end it all comes together in a really satisfying way. Going for all the achievements makes it even more fun. Highly recommended for indie and horror fans!  Absolutely loved it!",
      "timestamp_created": 1774112166
    },
